    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/948b9256c27c6066e23ab68c0f75159f.poster.avif?t=1769073550\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/948b9256c27c6066e23ab68c0f75159f.webm?t=1769073550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/948b9256c27c6066e23ab68c0f75159f.mp4?t=1769073550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《故障星系》是一款双摇杆Roguelike射击游戏，拥有<strong>物理驱动的战斗系统</strong>。使用重力枪，利用物理机制，抓取岩石和地雷并从竞技场墙壁上弹射出去。接住敌人的火箭弹并扔回他们脸上，甚至可以抓起敌人互相撞击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/321b6b11e98d8eacb064812159bb9684.webp?t=1769073550\" width=374 height=11 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/31b14ca66782bd1782a1d2b43c1cb970.poster.avif?t=1769073550\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/31b14ca66782bd1782a1d2b43c1cb970.webm?t=1769073550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/31b14ca66782bd1782a1d2b43c1cb970.mp4?t=1769073550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/289edfd8bb73c7d16e4a3e5fa94fb771.avif?t=1769073550\" width=622 height=77 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2D太空Roguelite</strong> - 体验刺激的双摇杆射击玩法，结合roguelite的无限重玩性和永久死亡的紧张挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物理驱动战斗</strong> - 挥舞强大的重力枪操控战场，投掷巨大的小行星，并将敌人的导弹反击回去</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多部件敌人</strong> - 策略性地逐块拆解敌人，利用他们的弱点同时避开重装甲防御</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态探索</strong> - 深入神秘故障的星系世界，探索隐藏秘密和珍贵物品，开辟你的独特路线</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能力与道具</strong> - 在每次游戏中通过多样的升级路径自定义你的玩法。解锁新能力并尝试创意组合，打造你的终极Build </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/321b6b11e98d8eacb064812159bb9684.webp?t=1769073550\" width=374 height=11 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/85e737ead6fa494fcd3d0d448ff76d2b.poster.avif?t=1769073550\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/85e737ead6fa494fcd3d0d448ff76d2b.webm?t=1769073550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536620/extras/85e737ead6fa494fcd3d0d448ff76d2b.mp4?t=1769073550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
